      <title>London Ruby User Group (LRUG) talk June 2017: How to use React with Rails</title>
      <description>&lt;div&gt;I gave a talk titled 'How to use React with Rails' at the June meetup of the&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="http://lrug.org/"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;London Ruby User Group (LRUG)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;You can watch the talk here&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://skillsmatter.com/skillscasts/10338-using-react-js-with-ruby-on-rails-apps"&gt;on the Skills Matter website&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;The&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://speakerdeck.com/hrishimittal/how-to-use-react-with-rails-talk-at-lrug-june-2017"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;slides are on Speakerdeck&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;If you enjoyed the talk, check out my&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://learnetto.com/users/hrishio/courses/the-free-react-on-rails-5-course"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Free React on Rails course&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;and&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://learnetto.com/users/hrishio/courses/the-complete-react-on-rails-5-course"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Complete React on Rails course&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;strong&gt;.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href="https://assets.learnetto.com/blog/2017-07-06/1499338101667-Screen%20Shot%202017-07-06%20at%2011.47.24.png" data-trix-attachment="{&amp;quot;contentType&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;image/png&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;filename&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;Screen Shot 2017-07-06 at 11.47.24.png&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;filesize&amp;quot;:6399382,&amp;quot;height&amp;quot;:1878,&amp;quot;href&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;https://assets.learnetto.com/blog/2017-07-06/1499338101667-Screen%20Shot%202017-07-06%20at%2011.47.24.png&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;url&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;https://assets.learnetto.com/blog/2017-07-06/1499338101667-Screen%20Shot%202017-07-06%20at%2011.47.24.png&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;width&amp;quot;:3354}" data-trix-content-type="image/png" data-trix-attributes="{&amp;quot;caption&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;\&amp;quot;How to use React with Rails\&amp;quot; LRUG June 2017&amp;quot;}"&gt;&lt;figure class="attachment attachment-preview png"&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.learnetto.com/blog/2017-07-06/1499338101667-Screen%20Shot%202017-07-06%20at%2011.47.24.png" width="3354" height="1878"&gt;&lt;figcaption class="caption caption-edited"&gt;"How to use React with Rails" LRUG June 2017&lt;/figcaption&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
